msgid "Good-bye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "Snap out of it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid "Your boss was MAD."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid "Try harder next time..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Oasis042_near00"
msgid "What happened to Barta?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Oasis042_near01"
msgid "You lousy lot..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: sound
#. 5: text_size
#. 6: pause (longer)
#. 7: text_size
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Whuh...<2.pa> Whah...<3.pa>\n"
"<4.so><5.te_si>WHAAAAT?!<6.pa><7.te_si>\n"
"Barta didn't come back AGAIN?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm afraid this time she went to \n"
"investigate the <2.se_co>leviathan bones <3.re_co>in the\n"
"southwest..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk04"
msgid "<1.so>I... I tried to stop her..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>But obviously it didn't work because\n"
"she's not here!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Yes, nobody would dare! And not only\n"
"that, but it's an <2.se_co>extremely hot zone<3.re_co>, so\n"
"we wouldn't last long there in our gear..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: text_size
#. 5: text_size
#. 6: pause (longer)
#. 7: sound
#. 8: sound
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You... <2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>You <4.te_si>IDIOTS!<5.te_si><6.pa> \n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>That scatterbrain wouldn't even realize\n"
"she was walking into danger! I mean,\n"
"you know that, right?!\n"
"<8.so>Why, it was just the other day she ran\n"
"off and got captured by the Yiga!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: set_colour (grey)
#. 4: text_size
#. 5: text_size
#. 6: reset_colour
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I've had it up to here with you lot!\n"
"You're walking embarrassments!\n"
"And now Barta has gone missing...<2.pa>\n"
"If the chief finds out, what do you think\n"
"she's going to say? \n"
"\n"
"<3.se_co><4.te_si>Must do something before we get found "
"out...<5.te_si><6.re_co>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ugh... I guess Barta will be Barta, and\n"
"you all aren't going to change...<2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"But still, why does she have to go and\n"
"get in trouble like this all the time..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ahhh... What do I do... Poor Barta is\n"
"in trouble again..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk11"
msgid ""
"<1.so>What do I do about Barta?\n"
"Do I say something? Or nothing..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
msgctxt "Oasis042_talk12"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Well, yeah...<2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>But... Everyone knows that area is the\n"
"domain of the <4.se_co>Molduga<5.re_co>, so who would\n"
"figure she'd even go close to there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Valetta_near00"
msgid "Ugh..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: single_choice
msgctxt "Valetta_talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Are you...a fairy? An angel?\n"
"Are you here to guide my passage?\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>...Everything's going hazy...\n"
"This might be the end...<3.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (longer)
#. 5: text_size
#. 6: text_size
msgctxt "Valetta_talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ahh... If only I could've eaten a\n"
"<2.se_co>hearty durian <3.re_co>one last time...<4.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<5.te_si>A hearty durian...\n"
"A hearty durian...<6.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Valetta_talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ahh, spirits of the Goddess... Before you\n"
"bear me away, could I just have a bite of\n"
"delicious durian...\n"
"Just one taste of a <2.se_co>hearty durian<3.re_co>..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: choice
msgctxt "Valetta_talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ahh, spirits of the Goddess... Before you\n"
"take me from this world, if I could just\n"
"taste fruit...\n"
"Just one last bite of a <2.se_co>hearty durian<3.re_co>...<4.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Valetta_talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>S-spirit... Just one bite would do...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"A little <2.se_co>hearty durian <3.re_co>for me...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Before my last sav'orq..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: pause (longer)
#. 4: sound
#. 5: sound
#. 6: sound
#. 7: single_choice
msgctxt "Valetta_talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hah...<2.pa> I've returned from the brink of\n"
"death thanks to you...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"Sarqso!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>Huh? Is that you I spoke to before?\n"
"<5.so>So you are actually a voe...\n"
"\n"
"I thought you were a bit muscular for a\n"
"Hylian vai.\n"
"\n"
"But don't worry, your secret is safe with\n"
"me. I owe you my life, after all!\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>Hah... Anyway, I'm totally exhausted.\n"
"Maybe I'll rest just a little longer then\n"
"head home.<7.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Valetta_talk06"
msgid "<1.so>Huh? So...they knew <2.pa>I snuck off..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: text_size
#. 2: set_colour (grey)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: sound
#. 5: text_size
msgctxt "Valetta_talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.te_si><2.se_co>...Oh, I am in such trouble...<3.re_co>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<4.so><5.te_si>Yep, looks like I'd better go on ahead.\n"
"See you later and sav'orq!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: pause (longer)
#. 4: sound
#. 5: sound
#. 6: single_choice
msgctxt "Valetta_talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hah...<2.pa> I've returned from death's door\n"
"thanks to you...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"I guess it really was reckless of me to\n"
"come here without the proper gear...\n"
"\n"
"Sarqso!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>Looks like you just keep saving me, huh?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>Hah... Anyway, I'm completely spent.\n"
"Maybe I'll rest just a little longer and\n"
"then head home.<6.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: pause (longer)
#. 4: sound
#. 5: sound
#. 6: single_choice
msgctxt "Valetta_talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hahh...<2.pa> I've come back from the brink\n"
"thanks to you...<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"I guess it really was reckless of me to\n"
"come here without the proper gear...\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>...But you don't seem to have the proper\n"
"gear, either. It's kind of amazing that you\n"
"even made it here to be honest.\n"
"<5.so>Hahh... Anyway, I'm absolutely beat.\n"
"Maybe I'll rest just a little longer and\n"
"then head home.<6.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (longer)
#. 5: set_colour (blue)
#. 6: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I guess I can't sit on this any longer... \n"
"\n"
"\n"
"There's a rumor that a fairy lives in the\n"
"<2.se_co>leviathan bones <3.re_co>southwest of town...\n"
"\n"
"I thought it was something that Barta\n"
"might be interested in...<4.pa>\n"
"\n"
"But that area is also known as the home\n"
"of the <5.se_co>Molduga<6.re_co>... \n"
"\n"
"Going there alone would be \n"
"unthinkable..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: sound
#. 7: set_colour (blue)
#. 8: reset_colour
#. 9: single_choice
msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Great, now my senior officer Liana is\n"
"steamed at me... Well, as she should be,\n"
"I guess...\n"
"I got in trouble over something related to\n"
"Barta with our <2.se_co>squad leader,<3.re_co> <4.se_co>Teake<5.re_co>,\n"
"before as well, and she was really mad...\n"
"<6.so>But I did kind of try to sort of stop her, \n"
"you know!\n"
"\n"
"I told her it was a <7.se_co>region of extreme heat<8.re_co>\n"
"and that she should equip herself\n"
"appropriately if she was going there...<9.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh! What a courageous vai! I heard\n"
"from Barta! She said you found her!\n"
"\n"
"I told her you were as dependable as a\n"
"Champion!<2.so> If you were a Gerudo vai,\n"
"I'd want you in my troop!\n"
"Anyway, close one, huh? Looks like I got\n"
"out of this without getting chewed out by\n"
"our troop leader!\n"
"<3.so>You must be worn out, right? Here, take\n"
"this as thanks! Buy yourself something\n"
"nice in the market!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Well, it looks like Barta at least feels\n"
"bad about what happened this time...\n"
"What a mess, though.<2.pa>\n"
"And you know the worst part? Even a vai\n"
"like Barta, who's all over the place, is\n"
"popular with the voe. \n"
"<3.so>I don't get it."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>...If you think about it, making your way\n"
"across the desert like that is really\n"
"pretty impressive.\n"
"<2.so>I wonder if that means Barta is actually\n"
"really strong..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>When you showed up, I thought for a\n"
"second that maybe the voe of my dreams\n"
"had come along.\n"
"<2.so>Speaking of which, I wonder how things\n"
"are going for that voe-crazy Perda...\n"
"I wonder if she's met the one yet...\n"
"Maybe once everyone forgets how in\n"
"trouble I am, I should head out and look\n"
"for my special someone..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If you hadn't come along when you did...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I would have had to say my eternal\n"
"sav'orq before I'd even met the voe of\n"
"my dreams...\n"
"<2.so>From the bottom of my heart, sarqso.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>Speaking of which, I wonder how things\n"
"are going for that voe-crazy Perda...\n"
"I wonder if she's met the one yet...\n"
"Maybe once everyone forgets how in\n"
"trouble I am, I should head out and look\n"
"for my special someone..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid "<1.so>ARGH!"
msgstr ""

